 Smart Study Planner

Overview

StudyFlow is a web app that helps students organize their study tasks, track progress, and improve productivity. It includes a planner, Pomodoro timer, daily progress tracker, and a 30-day challenge for consistent learning.

Features

Task Planner: Add, complete, and delete tasks.

Daily Progress: Shows completed vs pending tasks with visual charts.

Pomodoro Timer: Start, pause, and reset study sessions.

30-Day Challenge: Track daily study habits with interactive grid.

Dark/Light Mode: Switch theme according to preference.

User Login/Register: Save and manage account data locally.


Technologies Used

HTML

CSS (Flexbox & Grid)

JavaScript (DOM manipulation, events, localStorage)

Font Awesome icons


How to Run

1. Open the project folder.


2. Open index.html in a web browser.


3. Use the planner and other tools to manage tasks and track progress.



Future Improvements

Add backend for multiple users.

Customizable Pomodoro timer.

Notifications and reminders.

Analytics dashboard for long-term progress.
